---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="SMS Terms & Conditions | CoverToday Insurance" description="CoverToday Insurance SMS/text messaging terms: consent, message frequency, STOP and HELP keywords, message and data rates, and privacy.">
  <section class="hero"><div class="wrap">
    <h1>SMS Terms &amp; Conditions</h1>
    <p class="sub">How text messaging works with CoverToday Insurance Agency.</p>
  </div></section>

  <section><div class="wrap" style="max-width:820px">
    <p style="color:var(--muted)">Last updated: June 15, 2026</p>

    <h2 class="sec">Program description</h2>
    <p>When you provide your mobile number and opt in, CoverToday Insurance Agency ("CoverToday," "we") may send you text (SMS/MMS) messages related to insurance quotes, applications, policy service, certificates of insurance, appointment reminders, and — if you separately consent — promotional offers.</p>

    <h2 class="sec">Consent</h2>
    <p>By providing your phone number and checking the consent box on our forms, you agree to receive text messages from CoverToday at the number provided. Consent is not a condition of purchase. Marketing and non-marketing consent are requested separately, and you may choose either, both, or neither.</p>

    <h2 class="sec">Message frequency</h2>
    <p>Message frequency varies based on your interactions with us (for example, when you request a quote or we follow up on documents).</p>

    <h2 class="sec">Message &amp; data rates</h2>
    <p>Message and data rates may apply, depending on your mobile carrier and plan.</p>

    <h2 class="sec">Opt out — reply STOP</h2>
    <p>You can cancel SMS messages at any time by replying <strong>STOP</strong> to any message. After you send STOP, we will send a confirmation and then stop sending messages. To opt back in, reply <strong>START</strong>.</p>

    <h2 class="sec">Help — reply HELP</h2>
    <p>For help, reply <strong>HELP</strong> to any message, call us at (310) 299-5555, or email <a href="mailto:info@covertoday.com">info@covertoday.com</a>.</p>

    <h2 class="sec">Privacy</h2>
    <p>We never sell your personal information or share it with third parties for their own marketing. Mobile information will not be shared with third parties/affiliates for marketing or promotional purposes. See our <a href="/privacy-policy">Privacy Policy</a> for details.</p>

    <h2 class="sec">Carriers</h2>
    <p>Supported carriers are not liable for delayed or undelivered messages.</p>

    <h2 class="sec">Contact</h2>
    <p>CoverToday Insurance Agency, 272 S Rampart Blvd, Los Angeles, CA 90057 · (310) 299-5555 · info@covertoday.com · CA License #0K77310.</p>
  </div></section>
</Base>
